These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, juice, lemonade
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, chess, woodworking, skydiving
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is chess##2
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
3. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking almond-milk##7
4. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | juice | lemonade       | fanta | almond-milk        |
| Hobby      | woodworking  | chess | skydiving        | collecting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, lizard, cat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, lacrosse, weightlifting, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the owner of the lizard##7
2. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
3. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | lizard | chinchilla       | cat         | hamster     |
| Sport   | lacrosse   | sailing | weightlifting | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, spy, drama, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, rock, funk, r&b
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of r&b is somewhere between the fan of rock and the fan of disco##7
3. the fan of funk is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the fan of disco is somewhere between the fan of r&b and the person watching spy movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | satire | drama | zombie  |
| Music-Genre   | funk | disco  | r&b   | rock |

