.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, filmmaking, singing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, tennis, cycling, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's hobby is singing##7
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | hiking | gardening | singing       | filmmaking |
| Sport   | tennis      | badminton   | cycling | handball  |

