.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, photography, hiking, baking
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, pakistani, indonesian, egyptian
1. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
2. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the egyptian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##7
5. the egyptian is on the left of the indonesian##1
6. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the egyptian##5
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | hiking | filmmaking   | baking | photography |
| Nationality   | mexican      | pakistani | egyptian      | indonesian |

