.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, coffee
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, turkish, french, australian
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the french##1
2. the french is the person drinking coffee##1
3. the turkish is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the australian##3
6. the australian is somewhere between the colombian and the turkish##7
7. the french is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | juice      | hot-chocolate | coffee     |
| Nationality   | colombian    | australian | turkish   | french |

