.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, kiwi, peas, pomegranate
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, australian, egyptian, brazilian
1. the colombian is on the far left##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the australian##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left or far right##3
4. the brazilian is somewhere between the person eating radish and the person eating peas##7
5. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the person eating peas##5
6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the egyptian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | pomegranate    | radish   | kiwi | peas  |
| Nationality   | colombian | egyptian | brazilian    | australian |

