.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, malaysian, pakistani, german
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, turtle, bird
1. the malaysian is not the owner of the bird##6
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
3. the german is the owner of the turtle##1
4. the pakistani is somewhere between the german and the indonesian##7
5. the malaysian is on the left of the indonesian##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | german | pakistani | malaysian | indonesian |
| Pet           | turtle   | bird    | goldfish       | goat  |

