.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, software-developer, journalist, project-manager
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, reggae, house, disco
1. the bartender is not the fan of soul##6
2. the journalist is on the right of the bartender##1
3. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the bartender##3
4. the bartender is on the right of the fan of disco##1
5. the journalist is somewhere between the fan of disco and the software-developer##7
6. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan of house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | project-manager | bartender | journalist | software-developer |
| Music-Genre   | disco         | house      | soul | reggae            |

