1. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the owner of the goat##7
2. the person watching scientific movies is not the owner of the ferret##6
3. the owner of the bird is not the person watching disaster movies##6
4. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
5. the person watching spy movies is the owner of the fish##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | time-travel | scientific | disaster |
| Pet           | fish    | bird   | goat  | ferret      |

