1. the fan of funk is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching satire movies and the fan of reggae##2
6. the fan of disco is somewhere between the fan of reggae and the person watching satire movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | western | martial-arts | satire | superhero   |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | disco      | blues      | funk |

