.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, rock-climbing, board-games, singing
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, snowmobile, roller, boat
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the roller is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | singing | camping | rock-climbing | board-games |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | boat      | snowmobile        | roller  |

