4. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
