2. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person driving the boat and the person driving the tram##2
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
5. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
6. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage    | coffee   | water  | iced-tea  | 7up |
| Transport   | car | boat | scooter | tram    |

