.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, frog, rat, cat
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, jet-ski, train, helicopter
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the owner of the frog##7
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
5. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | frog    | rat | cat     | goat |
| Transport   | train | helicopter  | jet-ski | skateboard |

 